\begin{align}\dbinom{n}{k}\dbinom{k}{m}&=\dfrac{n!}{k!\, n-k!}\dfrac{k!}{m!\, (k-m)!}\\&=\dfrac{n!}{(n-k)!\,(k-m)!\,m!}\\&=\dfrac{n!}{m!\,(n-m)!}\dfrac{(n-m)!}{(n-k)!\,(k-m)!}\\&=\dbinom{n}{m}\dbinom{n-m}{k-m}\end{align}
